    <!-- ── TRUST FAQ ── -->
    <section class="pdp-faq lp-faq">
      <div class="pdp-faq-inner">
        <div class="pdp-faq-head">
          <span class="pdp-faq-eyebrow">First-Time Buyer Questions</span>
          <h2 class="pdp-faq-title">Why this beats a beer at the BBQ.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="pdp-faq-grid">

          <details class="pdp-faq-item" open>
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg></span>
              <span>Is this actually 0% alcohol?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>Yes — completely non-alcoholic.</strong> 0.0% ABV. Safe to drink while driving, at work, around the kids, or pregnant (always check with your doctor on the last one). Looks like a craft cocktail, tastes refreshing, but won't put you on the couch.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/></svg></span>
              <span>Will I feel anything at all?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>20–40 minutes in.</strong> Lion's Mane brings clear, calm focus. Cordyceps adds steady energy. Reishi takes the edge off without sedating you. It's a present, sociable feeling — not a buzz, not a stimulant rush.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></span>
              <span>What if I don't like the taste?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>30-day full refund, no return needed.</strong> Email <a href="mailto:orders@livehappie.com">orders@livehappie.com</a> within 30 days. Tastes like sparkling juice — Blue Razz is tart and candy-bright. No earthy mushroom flavor.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v8"/><path d="M5.6 5.6a9 9 0 1 0 12.8 0"/></svg></span>
              <span>How is this different from non-alcoholic beer?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>NA beer mimics beer; Happie actually does something.</strong> Most non-alcoholic beers are dealcoholized regular beer — same taste, zero effect. Happie has <strong>2,000mg of functional mushrooms</strong> per can that deliver real focus, energy, and calm. It's the difference between "fake beer" and "real wellness drink that happens to fit the alcohol-free occasion."</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="6" width="15" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M16 10h4l3 3v4h-7"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="19.5" r="1.5"/><circle cx="20.5" cy="19.5" r="1.5"/></svg></span>
              <span>Will it arrive in time for July 4th?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>Order by June 30 for guaranteed July 4th delivery.</strong> Standard shipping is 3–5 business days and ships within 1 business day from our Northern California warehouse. Need it faster? Express is $15 at checkout (2 business days). Free shipping on every order — no minimum.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-12V5l-8-3-8 3v5c0 8 8 12 8 12z"/></svg></span>
              <span>Is it actually safe? Has it been tested?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>Every batch is third-party tested at KCA Laboratories</strong> (ISO/IEC 17025:2017 accredited, Nicholasville KY). We test for heavy metals, 66 pesticides, microbials, mycotoxins, and residual solvents. <a href="/pages/the-science#lab-results">Download the COA for the batch in your fridge →</a></p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg></span>
              <span>One can or one 6-pack — what's the right amount for a BBQ?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>One can per person, per ~2 hours.</strong> The effects of one can last 3–4 hours. For a 4-hour BBQ with 4 sober-curious adults, a 6-pack gets you through with extras. If you're hosting and want a stocked fridge for friends, grab the <a href="/products/happie-fungi-fusion-mushroom-drink-variety-pack">12-pack Variety Pack</a> — better value and lets guests pick their flavor.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="pdp-faq-item">
            <summary class="pdp-faq-q">
              <span class="pdp-faq-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg></span>
              <span>Will I get a hangover? Can I drink it before driving?</span>
              <span class="pdp-faq-chev"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pdp-faq-a">
              <p><strong>Zero hangover. Zero impairment.</strong> 0.0% ABV means it's legally a soft drink — same as a sparkling water. Safe to drink and drive home, safe before work, safe while operating machinery. The Lion's Mane focus actually <em>improves</em> reaction time vs nothing. The next morning, no fog, no regret.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div><!-- /product-page -->

</div><!-- /lp-july4 -->

